These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, entrepreneur, musician, bartender
House: colonial, victorian, craftsman, futuristic
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, cola, sprite, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the victorian house##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the colonial house##1
3. the musician is on the far left##1
4. the analyst is on the far right##1
5. the victorian house is between the person drinking sprite and the entrepreneur##2
6. the person drinking cola is the craftsman house##1
7. the colonial house is on the right of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Job        | musician | bartender  | entrepreneur | analyst  |
| House         | futuristic    | victorian  | colonial       | craftsman     |
| Beverage   | sprite     | soy-milk | hot-chocolate       | cola |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, police-officer, coach, writer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, d&b, funk, rock
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, emerald, coral, lavender
1. the police-officer is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the architect##1
3. the person who likes emerald is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes lavender is between the fan rock and the writer##2
5. the fan rock is the person who likes emerald##1
6. the fan hip-hop is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
7. the fan funk is the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Job         | police-officer | architect    | writer  | coach |
| Music-Genre   | rock  | hip-hop  | d&b   | funk    |
| Color         | emerald | lavender | fuchsia | coral      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, taxi, tram, train
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, montecristo, bluemaster, chaman
4 different games are played: scrabble, whist, backgammon, snooker
1. the person playing whist is between the person playing snooker and the person driving the taxi##2
2. the prince-smoker is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
3. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
4. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
5. the montecristo-smoker is on the far left##1
6. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
7. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Transport      | taxi | train         | snowmobile   | tram    |
| Cigar         | montecristo | chaman | prince | bluemaster |
| Game   | backgammon   | whist        | snooker      | scrabble   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, accountant, doctor, freelancer
House: art-deco, craftsman, futuristic, farmhouse
City: london, miami, nizza, new-york
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to london is between the person traveling to new-york and the freelancer##2
3. the doctor is on the right of the craftsman house##1
4. the person traveling to london is on the right of the futuristic house##1
5. the doctor is on the right of the firefighter##1
6. the person traveling to new-york is between the art-deco house and the person traveling to miami##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Job   | freelancer        | accountant   | firefighter | doctor |
| House         | futuristic | art-deco | craftsman    | farmhouse |
| City     | nizza       | london     | new-york       | miami    |

