.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, pomegranate, cranberry, peas
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, zinnia, iris, begonia
4 different pets are kept: frog, rat, guinea-pig, mouse
1. the owner of the mouse is between the person eating nectarine and the person eating pomegranate##2
2. the owner of the mouse is the person eating peas##1
3. the person who growsiris is on the far right##1
4. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
7. the owner of the mouse is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the person who growsdaffodil##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Food   | nectarine | peas      | pomegranate       | cranberry   |
| Flower      | daffodil   | zinnia  | begonia | iris     |
| Pet      | rat     | mouse | guinea-pig        | frog |

