.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, bridge, whist, poker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, mystery, romance, musical
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, hot-chocolate, water, sprite
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person drinking water##1
3. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is between the person watching musical movies and the person drinking water##2
6. the person playing bridge is between the person playing backgammon and the person playing whist##2
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Game    | whist | bridge  | backgammon | poker      |
| Movie-Genre   | romance  | musical  | documentary | mystery |
| Beverage   | sprite | iced-tea | hot-chocolate | water     |

