.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, skydiving, baking, collecting
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, august, may, november
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, sprite, soy-milk
1. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person drinking sprite is the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in may##2
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby          | baking  | skydiving    | collecting | video-games  |
| Birthday   | may | november       | august        | january    |
| Beverage         | cola | coffee | soy-milk  | sprite |

