.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
4 different games are played: whist, mah-jongg, billiard, chess
House: victorian, modern, gothic-revival, craftsman
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, handball, biathlon, water-polo
1. the craftsman house is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the modern house is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person playing mah-jongg##2
3. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the craftsman house is on the right of the person playing chess##1
6. the person playing billiard is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Game         | chess  | mah-jongg | billiard | whist |
| House   | victorian  | craftsman | modern   | gothic-revival         |
| Sport           | snowboarding | biathlon  | handball   | water-polo      |

