.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
4 different games are played: domino, mah-jongg, backgammon, whist
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, martial-arts, western, mystery
City: miami, prague, marseilles, new-york
1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person playing domino##1
3. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person watching western movies is the person playing mah-jongg##1
5. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing whist##1
6. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1
7. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person watching adventure movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Game          | whist  | domino    | backgammon | mah-jongg       |
| Movie-Genre         | mystery | martial-arts | adventure  | western |
| City   | marseilles   | new-york      | prague  | miami     |

