The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, house, trance, metal
1. the owner of the ferret is on the far left##1
2. the person playing whist is on the far left##1
3. the person playing monopoly is between the person playing scrabble and the owner of the lizard##2
4. the fan house is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the far right##1
6. the fan house is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
7. the fan metal is the owner of the ferret##1
8. the fan classical is the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Game          | whist      | backgammon | monopoly | scrabble |
| Pet         | ferret   | lizard  | snake | mouse |
| Music-Genre   | metal | classical   | house | trance |

