The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, september, october, may
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, pop, salsa, country
1. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
2. the fan salsa is the oliveros-smoker##1
3. the fan folk is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in october##2
4. the person who's birthday is in october is between the fan folk and the montecristo-smoker##2
5. the person who's birthday is in october is the fan country##1
6. the person who's birthday is in april is the fan pop##1
7. the person who's birthday is in may is the fan folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Cigar    | montecristo  | tiparillo | blend | oliveros     |
| Birthday   | april | october   | may  | september    |
| Music-Genre     | pop        | country       | folk      | salsa |

