The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, jazz, country, disco
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, cauliflower, pepper, blueberry
1. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
2. the person eating blueberry is between the person who likes green and the fan house##2
3. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who likes green##1
4. the person who likes grey is the person eating pepper##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the fan jazz##1
6. the person who likes aquamarine is the fan country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
| Color   | grey | aquamarine  | green       | blue   |
| Music-Genre      | house     | country | jazz | disco |
| Food        | pepper        | blueberry | kiwi     | cauliflower |

