There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, polish, canadian, indian
1. the person who growspoppy is the indian##1
2. the canadian is the owner of the goat##1
3. the canadian is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
4. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the indian##1
5. the polish is between the person who growssunflower and the owner of the goat##2
6. the indian is on the far right##1
7. the polish is the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Pet           | hedgehog | guinea-pig | goat    | frog   |
| Flower   | sunflower      | lily   | begonia | poppy |
| Nationality     | egyptian     | polish       | canadian        | indian    |

