.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-18::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, scientist, dressmaker, firefighter
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, azure, grey, blood-red
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, climbing, golf, cricket
1. the person who likes grey is the scientist##1
2. the analyst is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
3. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the dressmaker##1
4. the analyst is between the person who likes grey and the person who likes lavender##2
5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the firefighter##1
6. the person who's sport is cricket is between the scientist and the person who's sport is parkour##2
7. the person who likes blood-red is the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Job      | dressmaker | analyst | scientist     | firefighter   |
| Color   | lavender | blood-red        | grey  | azure  |
| Sport           | parkour      | cricket         | climbing | golf |

