.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, surfing, baseball, basketball
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, august, september, january
4 different games are played: go, snooker, poker, domino
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far right##1
5. the person playing domino is the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person playing poker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Sport        | basketball | surfing | tennis | baseball |
| Birthday         | march       | august     | september   | january   |
| Game   | go | snooker | poker | domino |

 